  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "August 9, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "b7c [REDACTED] make the following voluntary statement",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "to SA [REDACTED] of the Federal Bureau of Investigation.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "In the early part of June 1947 we picked up some strange rock formations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "from a gravel pit on Maury Island, Washington. We sent a box (cigar)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "b7c of these fragments to [REDACTED] of Venture Magazine at Evanston Illinois",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "to have it analyzed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Later [REDACTED] wrote and asked for additional samples stating that he had",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "b7c failed to have them analyzed.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Around the later part of June a few days after the first disc stories",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "b7c started [REDACTED] contacted us by phone. He told us not to tell the news-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "papers about the fragments and he would pay for an exclusive story if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "the fragments could be from a flying disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "One of us told him the fragments could have been from a flying disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Just after our phone conversation [REDACTED] wrote a letter to [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "[REDACTED] setting out some notes etc. regarding the fragments and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "indicating they could have come from flying discs. b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "The next thing we heard was about the first of July when we got a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Trans Ocean Press telegram from Chicago asking [unclear] about these flying b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "disc fragments. We told them to forget the entire matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "The next we heard of these fragments was when we were called by b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED] to meet with him in the Winthrop Hotel on July 31, 1947",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "We told him exactly how we had found the fragments and had forwarded them",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "to [REDACTED] to be analyzed. b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "The above is the entire and true story as regards our connection with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "the flying disc stories etc. which originated over the ore samples which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "we sent to be analyzed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "[REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "[REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "F.B.I. Seattle 8/9/47.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
  ],
